originalSql:
SELECT 
    n.n_name AS nation_name,
    r.r_name AS region_name,
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_revenue
FROM 
    lineitem l
JOIN 
    orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN 
    customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
JOIN 
    supplier s ON l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON l.l_partkey = ps.ps_partkey AND s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
JOIN 
    nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN 
    region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
WHERE 
    o.o_orderdate >= DATE '1993-01-01' AND o.o_orderdate < DATE '1994-01-01'
GROUP BY 
    n.n_name, r.r_name
ORDER BY 
    total_revenue DESC

INNER JOIN "customer" ON "orders"."o_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"
INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineitem"."l_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "lineitem"."l_partkey" = "s1"."ps_partkey" AND "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "s1"."ps_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "supplier"."s_nationkey" = "nation"."n_nationkey"
INNER JOIN "region" ON "nation"."n_regionkey" = "region"."r_regionkey"
WHERE "orders"."o_orderdate" >= DATE '1993-01-01' AND "orders"."o_orderdate" < DATE '1994-01-01'
GROUP BY "nation"."n_name", "region"."r_name"
ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t4"

SELECT COALESCE("n_nationkey", "n_nationkey") AS "n_nationkey", "n_name", "n_regionkey", "n_comment"
FROM "nation"

SELECT COALESCE("t4"."NATION_NAME", "t4"."NATION_NAME") AS "NATION_NAME", "t4"."REGION_NAME", "t4"."TOTAL_REVENUE"
FROM (SELECT MIN("s1"."n_name") AS "NATION_NAME", MIN("region"."r_name") AS "REGION_NAME", SUM("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_REVENUE"
FROM "lineitem"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "lineitem"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey"
INNER JOIN "customer" ON "orders"."o_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"
INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineitem"."l_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "lineitem"."l_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey" AND "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "supplier"."s_nationkey" = "s1"."n_nationkey"
INNER JOIN "region" ON "s1"."n_regionkey" = "region"."r_regionkey"
WHERE "orders"."o_orderdate" >= DATE '1993-01-01' AND "orders"."o_orderdate" < DATE '1994-01-01'
GROUP BY "s1"."n_name", "region"."r_name"
ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t4"

SELECT COALESCE("r_regionkey", "r_regionkey") AS "r_regionkey", "r_name", "r_comment"
FROM "region"

SELECT COALESCE("t4"."NATION_NAME", "t4"."NATION_NAME") AS "NATION_NAME", "t4"."REGION_NAME", "t4"."TOTAL_REVENUE"
FROM (SELECT MIN("nation"."n_name") AS "NATION_NAME", MIN("s1"."r_name") AS "REGION_NAME", SUM("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_REVENUE"
FROM "lineitem"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "lineitem"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey"
INNER JOIN "customer" ON "orders"."o_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"
INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineitem"."l_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "lineitem"."l_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey" AND "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "supplier"."s_nationkey" = "nation"."n_nationkey"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "nation"."n_regionkey" = "s1"."r_regionkey"
WHERE "orders"."o_orderdate" >= DATE '1993-01-01' AND "orders"."o_orderdate" < DATE '1994-01-01'
GROUP BY "nation"."n_name", "s1"."r_name"
ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t4"
